## Image field

This field type can be used to upload (or select from media library) one or multiple images

## General options

- Field name
- Field key
- Description
- Is Required
- CSS Classes

## Specific options

- **Maximum file count:** Select the number of images allowed
- **Max file size (kB):**Set the max file size per attachment
- **Default image:**Upload a default image that will be output when no image is uploaded on this field
